<hr class="article-header__hr" />
<div class="article-header__subtitle">Conversation avec Michel Reckinger</div>
<h1 class="article-header__title">«Le gouvernement a du mal à se fixer des priorités»</h1>
<hr class="article-header__hr article-header__hr--author-top" />
<div class="article-header__author">
<div class="article-author">
<div class="article-author__picture"><img src="https://assets.paperjam.lu/xcrop/157/0/862/862/50/50/aHR0cHM6Ly9tYWlzb24tbW9kZXJuZS1wYXBlcmphbS1zYWxlc2ZvcmNlLW1tcHJvZC5zMy5ldS1jZW50cmFsLTEuYW1hem9uYXdzLmNvbS8vZ3VpZGUvZmlsZXMvNjRjNmFjZDk4YWQxNTY1ZWIwNTNlMjA0MWQ5Y2M4NzEuanBn" alt="Nathalie Reuter" loading="lazy" width="50" height="50" style="" class="external-image" /></div>
<div class="article-author__info">
<div class="article-author__info-text">
<p class="article-author__written-by">
Écrit par
<a href="/guide/biography/0581109907/nathalie-reuter" class="article-author__written-by article-author__name">
Nathalie Reuter</a>
</p>
<p>
Publié Le 27.11.2020
• Édité Le 27.11.2020
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="article-header__author-socials">
